items.name: Emo Philips
items.description: A computer once beat me at chess, but it was no match for me at kick boxing.

items.name: Ted Nelson
items.description: The good news about computers is that they do what you tell them to do. The bad news is that they do what you tell them to do.

items.name: Doug Larson
items.description: Home computers are being called upon to perform many new functions, including the consumption of homework formerly eaten by the dog.

items.name: Clifford Stoll
items.description: Treat your password like your toothbrush. Don't let anybody else use it, and get a new one every six months.

users.name: Michael Schaffner
users.description: Ouch! My cat just bit me!

users.name: Jennifer Schaffner
users.description: This dog sure likes her walks!

users.name: Emo Phillips
users.description: I wonder what will happen to the search now!
